## Work History

### Fortem - Manual QA Engineer (2018-2020)
Entry-level position in drone defense technology. Tested radar systems (R20/R30), autonomous drones, and Skydome command software. Developed expertise in networking fundamentals, DevOps tools, and automation. Created automated tests using Selenium and contributed to simulation software development. Trained new QA team members and established testing strategies.

**Key Skills:** Git, Selenium, Linux, Python, Node.js, Docker, Computer Networking, Bash, Wireshark, Nmap

### SocialClimb - QA Automation Engineer (2020-2022)
Led Selenium automation framework development using component-based architecture. Implemented distributed testing system with Master/Worker paradigm to handle 750+ automated tests. Created cloud-hosted test management platform inspired by TestRail for parallel test analysis. Conducted penetration testing, identifying vulnerabilities in role escalation and endpoint spoofing.

**Key Skills:** Selenium, Google Cloud, Docker, Postman, Penetration Testing

### SocialClimb - Full Stack Engineer (2022-2024)
Promoted to full-stack development role. Migrated local development to Docker containers for infrastructure consistency. Implemented EAV model for custom patient attributes with optimized SQL queries for millions of rows. Integrated Salesforce API for automated data syncing with robust logging. Created multiple SDKs for AWS Bedrock, Google Cloud, Anthropic Claude, Twilio, and Salesforce. Developed PHI data abstraction system for secure database testing.

**Key Skills:** Python, TypeScript, Angular, SQLAlchemy, MySQL, Docker, NGINX, Celery, Unit Testing

### RLDatix - Full Stack Engineer (2025-Present)
Leading development of AI-powered chatbot application for hospital incident reporting. Fixed contractor-delivered Go/React project within 2 months. Architected V2 system using Flask/Python backend, PostgreSQL, React with React Hook Form, and Tanstack Query. Implemented dynamic form creation with RAG-enabled fields and LangGraph integration with PostgreSQL conversation persistence.

**Key Skills:** LangGraph, React, React Hook Form, Tanstack Query, PostgreSQL, LLMs, Vector Embeddings, RAG Implementation
